Name: Cat's Copper Treat
Desc: Cheap treat from a cheap hooman

Name: Cat's Silver Treat
Desc: Good treat from a hard working hooman

Name: Risalia Copper Thorn
Desc: Coppers shed sweat and blood to earn a living, just like plucking roses with one's bare hands. Risalia will never forget its people and will remember them through Copper Thorns... though will those of nobility deal in couple... or will they leave the thorns to the gardeners and bask in the flowers?

Name: Risalia Silver Leaf
Desc: The craft and savy merchants of Risalia are always shuffling goods arounds and are to the nation what petals are to a Rose! Risalia graces their efforts with Silver Leaves!

Name: Risalia Gold Rose
Desc: Ah... Risalia's beautiful roses... Though Red they are, their luster is just as magnificant as a mountain of gold! The king is a gardener, and the more roses he plants, the wealthier Risalia is! Let it forever be remembered that Risalia will never lack Golden Roses!

Name: Risalia Platinum Griffin
Desc: Only when princess accepts your 13th Rose, will you earn the grace of her hand and the honor of having her in your garden. 13 Noble Roses dot the royal garden where the Royal Griffin resides, ever watchful. Risalia's most exalted coin, the Platinum Griffin, is one of honor far beyond its mere value!
